question: Show photographers and videographers who charged 500.
sql_query1:
SELECT Photographers.photographerName as name
FROM Photographers
WHERE Photographers.price = 500
UNION
SELECT Videographers.videographerName as name
FROM Videographers
WHERE Videographers.price = 500
sql_query2:
SELECT Photographers.photographerName as name
FROM Photographers
UNION
SELECT Videographers.videographerName as name
FROM Videographers
WHERE Videographers.price = 500
interpretation1: Which photographers charged 500 and which videographers charged the same price?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all photographers and also provide a list of all videographers who charged 500.
